Common.Highlight.Common.Text: One of QLD's fastest growing regions

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Colliers International and CBRE Gold Coast are pleased to present Coomera Town Centre South to the market. The 47.73ha* site is a true place-making destination development opportunity - strategically located in the high-growth Brisbane to Gold Coast corridor. 

The property benefits from a Preliminary Approval which has established the Coomera Activity Centre South Development Code and this approval allows for a range of code assessable uses and development types including residential, commercial and retail.

The Westfield Coomera Shopping Centre is located directly opposite the property on Foxwell Road. Spanning 59,000sqm of indoor-outdoor retail and leisure space, the centre features a Coles, Woolworths, Kmart, Target, JB Hi-Fi, Rebel, Event Cinemas and more than 150 specialty stores.  The Coomera Train and Bus Station is located within 100m of the property and provides high frequency connections to Brisbane and the Gold Coast.

For further information, please do not hesitate to contact the Exclusive Agents listed.

*Approx

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: SUITABLE TO A RANGE OF COMMERCIAL USERS

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE, are pleased to present the first release of Lots 28 – 30 for sale at The Link Coomera on behalf of Polaris Coomera Pty Ltd. These outstanding lots provide buyers with the opportunity to secure their piece of commercial land along the M1 Motorway between Coomera and Pimpama, two of the fastest growing suburbs on the Gold Coast.

The Lots benefits from being within close proximity to the new Westfield Coomera Shopping Centre, Coomera Railway Station and Exit 54.

The offering:

- Highway exposed land available for sale
- Mixed use / fringe business zoning allowing for a variety of users
- Direct and easy access to M1 Motorway at Exit 54
- Close proximity to Westfield Coomera and Coomera Rail Station

Available Lots for purchase:

- Lot 28 (5,512sqm*)
- Lot 29 (1.61HA*)
- Lot 30 (1.37HA*)
- All lots will be benched, levelled and serviced

For further information on this outstanding opportunity your exclusive agents
